<i>The cadence of your voice,
the vibrations.</i>

53:18.457 --> 53:22.661
<i>Like I know you
from the inside out.</i>

53:22.694 --> 53:29.267
<i>And so there's just this strong,
warm sense within me</i>

53:29.300 --> 53:32.771
<i>that you're beautiful.</i>

53:36.508 --> 53:40.579
<i>Someone seeing me like that.</i>

53:40.612 --> 53:42.614
<i>I think that's what I want.</i>

53:47.553 --> 53:50.422
