you're on your way.

53:52.791 --> 53:54.626
Amy's Advice?

53:54.660 --> 53:56.862
<i>Please.</i>

53:56.895 --> 54:00.832
Trust that warm feeling.

54:00.866 --> 54:02.601
Hold on to it.

54:05.269 --> 54:07.071
Let it lead you.

54:11.543 --> 54:14.479
<i>Thanks, Amy.</i>

54:14.513 --> 54:17.081
<i>Maybe if I'm lucky,
one day I'll end up like you.</i>

54:21.787 --> 54:24.790
Good luck, caller.

54:24.823 --> 54:28.860
<i>Oh,
and congratulations on retirement.</i>

54:28.894 --> 54:31.262
<i>I know some people
can be sad on days like this,</i>

54:31.295 --> 54:34.131
<i>but you did it!</i>

54:34.165 --> 54:36.133
<i>The hard part's over.</i>

54:36.167 --> 54:37.369
<i>Enjoy the victory lap.</i>

55:37.529 --> 55:39.196
Goddamn, Jesus Christ!

55:39.230 --> 55:41.400
Come on, close the door.

55:41.433 --> 55:42.701
Get on in here.

55:46.805 --> 55:51.308
Oh, what all did you do
this time?

55:51.343 --> 55:52.411
Aaron?

55:52.444 --> 55:53.612
Oh, he's already
in the sound booth.

55:53.645 --> 55:57.281
By the way, Bob wants to see you
in his office before the show.

55:57.314 --> 55:58.315
No.

55:58.350 --> 56:00.752
- No, no, no, no, no, no.
- That looks pretty nasty.

56:00.786 --> 56:02.721
Was it that raccoon again?

56:02.754 --> 56:05.424
That little dumpster bitch.

56:05.457 --> 56:07.993
Sure hope
he doesn't have rabies.

56:08.026 --> 56:08.960
What is going on?

56:08.994 --> 56:11.228
- What is going on?
- Hey, hey, hey, relax, Amy.

56:11.262 --> 56:13.665
The storm's got everyone
feelin' a little crazy.

56:13.699 --> 56:15.767
It's just one of those nights,
yeah?

56:18.737 --> 56:19.705
He did not.

56:19.738 --> 56:21.573
You have got to be kidding me.

56:21.606 --> 56:22.874
Hand to God, sweetheart.

56:22.908 --> 56:23.775
Hand to God.

56:25.644 --> 56:28.513
Amy, come in.

56:28.547 --> 56:30.549
Cutting it kind of close,
don't you think?

56:33.385 --> 56:34.886
Uh, Earth to Amy?

56:38.724 --> 56:40.324
Have you looked out a window?

56:40.358 --> 56:41.827
I can't say that I have.

56:41.860 --> 56:43.327
Got too good of a view
right here.

56:43.361 --> 56:45.030
Oh Robert, stop it.

56:45.063 --> 56:46.263
Please, sweetheart.

56:46.297 --> 56:48.800
- Call me "Bob".
- Bob.

56:48.834 --> 56:50.335
Sienna.

56:50.368 --> 56:52.504
Hmm, do you two know each other?

56:52.537 --> 56:54.740
Oh, no, I would've remembered.

56:54.773 --> 56:56.875
I grew up listening to you.

56:56.908 --> 56:58.944
Big fan.

56:58.977 --> 57:00.345
Then how do you know...

57:00.378 --> 57:02.614
Aaron uh, told me.

57:02.647 --> 57:03.482
I mean Ernie.

57:03.515 --> 57:04.616
Ernie.

57:04.649 --> 57:08.353
Are you alright, Amy?

57:08.386 --> 57:10.321
Never better.

57:10.355 --> 57:11.189
Alright, great.

57:11.223 --> 57:13.892
Well, she's gonna be
your shadow tonight,

57:13.925 --> 57:16.027
so make sure you show her
the ropes.

57:16.061 --> 57:18.396
Now, I don't want to impose.

57:18.430 --> 57:19.364
Nonsense.

57:19.397 --> 57:20.732
- She'd love to.
- I'd love to.

57:25.003 --> 57:28.373
Good on you, kiddo.

57:28.406 --> 57:30.976
You remember how it is.

57:31.009 --> 57:35.514
It's nice to have someone there
when you're transitioning.

57:35.547 --> 57:37.516
<i>You know,
that's what I like about you, Amy.</i>

57:37.549 --> 57:38.817
<i>You do it old school.</i>

57:43.355 --> 57:45.289
<i>Storm's really picking up, huh?</i>

57:47.492 --> 57:48.660
You want a bite?

57:48.693 --> 57:50.028
Garlic noodle.

57:52.697 --> 57:54.699
What's up with you tonight?

57:54.733 --> 57:59.437
Storm got you feeling
a little tweaked?

57:59.471 --> 58:01.373
Something like that.

58:01.406 --> 58:03.108
Oh, actually, you know what?

58:03.141 --> 58:04.943
It's probably solar flares.

58:04.976 --> 58:10.715
Bob said they've been causing
dead air for most of the day.

58:10.749 --> 58:11.550
I heard that.

58:11.583 --> 58:12.417
Yeah, but don't worry,

58:12.450 --> 58:14.686
we should be good
for the big show tonight.

58:16.621 --> 58:17.422
So sorry.

58:17.455 --> 58:18.657
Where do you want me?

58:22.627 --> 58:24.963
