Of course, what kind of party
would be this be

01:04:02.434 --> 01:04:03.768
without presents?

01:04:12.076 --> 01:04:12.777
Yeah, come on.

01:04:12.810 --> 01:04:14.279
Come on bring her up,
bring her up.

01:04:14.312 --> 01:04:15.780
Come on, man.

01:04:18.116 --> 01:04:20.752
