of a memento than a gift.

01:04:34.098 --> 01:04:35.334
I didn't wind it.

01:04:35.367 --> 01:04:36.968
Thought you'd like to spend
as much time

01:04:37.001 --> 01:04:39.237
in 10 minutes to midnight
as you could.

01:04:39.270 --> 01:04:40.171
Aaron.

01:04:40.205 --> 01:04:42.474
Oh,
he's got somethin' for you, too.

01:04:42.508 --> 01:04:44.376
But first, Sienna.

01:04:47.245 --> 01:04:49.047
Got a little sneaky
and found out the year

01:04:49.080 --> 01:04:50.081
you were born.

01:04:50.114 --> 01:04:52.784
Never would have guessed
with how beautiful you are.

01:04:52.817 --> 01:04:54.852
This was bottled
that same summer.

01:04:54.886 --> 01:04:57.523
May it fill your veins
with the weight of history.

01:05:10.802 --> 01:05:15.240
To close the circle, Amy,

01:05:15.273 --> 01:05:19.043
you're as beautiful
as the day you started here.

01:05:19.077 --> 01:05:22.414
And finally on behalf
of everyone here,

01:05:22.448 --> 01:05:26.751
